---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';
---

<PageLayout title="Terms & Conditions" description="Terms of service for Unleft.">
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 px-4">
      <Badge className="mb-6 bg-accent-primary/10 text-accent-glow border-none mx-auto w-fit font-gupter">Legal & Safety</Badge>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8 tracking-tighter">
        Terms & <span class="text-accent-primary">Conditions</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        The legal framework that governs our professional commitment to your projects.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-mono text-accent-glow uppercase tracking-widest">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-accent-primary/5 rounded-3xl blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
      <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-[#2D2D44] bg-[#0A0A0F]/60 p-8 md:p-12 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-2xl">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 md:gap-16 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">By accessing and using the Unleft website (Unleft.space), you accept and agree to be bound by these terms and conditions.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">2. Services</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">Unleft provides software development services including web development, game development, custom software, and AI-based systems. All project scopes, timelines, and pricing are agreed upon separately via project proposals.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and code, is the property of Unleft unless otherwise stated. Client deliverables are transferred upon full payment as defined in individual contracts.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">Unleft shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our website or services.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">5. Payment Terms</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">Payment terms, milestones, and refund policies are defined on a per-project basis in individual service agreements.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">6. Modifications</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">7. Contact</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">Questions about these terms can be directed to <a href="mailto:hello@unleft.space" class="text-accent-glow hover:text-accent-primary transition-colors underline underline-offset-4 decoration-accent-primary/30">hello@unleft.space</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
